\layout Section

Uplug tools
\layout Standard

To install Perl modules and scripts, cd to the uplug directory and do:
\layout LyX-Code

$ perl Makefile.PL
\layout LyX-Code

$ make
\layout LyX-Code

$ make install
\layout Standard

Some scripts in tools/ use bash (/bin/bash) You might have to adjust scripts
 in tools/ according to your installation.
\layout Standard

You should set the environment variable UPLUG_HOME to the directory where
 you have extracted the uplug files:
\layout LyX-Code

$ export UPLUG_HOME=/home/myhome/uplug
